oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Gov. Winfield Dunn (center, seated) signing a proclamation proclaiming the day Official Baton Twirling Day in Tennessee. Rita Garvey, Tennessee Dance Twirl Grand Champion, is shown on the right. Other individuals in the photo are not identified.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Rita Garvey Harmon trained with the Tennessee Twirling Institute. She was the reigning Tennessee Dance Twirl Grand Champion at the time this photograph was taken.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: RG 82: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Governors; Baton twirling; Sports; Proclamations
